message.content: cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR. The paper deals with visual question answering, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The proposed system also involves machine learning techniques (cs.AI, cs.LG) to predict answer agreement. Finally, the system can be applied to crowdsourcing (cs.IR) to efficiently collect answers to visual questions.
